{"tid":302597,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"興業太陽能：持69股可認購1股興業新材料","createTime":"2017-06-29T13:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T13:42:10.000Z","uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d162c4cff4df3d551f61eea80570faeae8011912","tid":302597,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T13:33:17.000Z","msg":"【750】興業太陽能：持69股可認購1股興業新材料<br />\n<br />\n[2017-06-28 20:40]<br />\n<br />\n興業太陽能(00750)宣布，分拆中國興業新材料控股於創業板上市，昨向聯交所提交聆訊後資料。<br />\n<br />\n此外，合資格興業太陽能股東優先發售的基準為，合資格興業太陽能股東於記錄日期下午4時30分，每持有69股興業太陽能股份的完整倍數，可認購一股預留股份。<br />\n<br />\n集團預期，合資格興業太陽能股東將獲邀申請合共1200萬股預留股份，相當於股份發售完成後經擴大股本的2.5%。（nc）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://vancouver.singtao.ca/1222522/2017-06-28/post-【750】興業太陽能：持69股可認購1股興業新材料/?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvancouver.singtao.ca%2F1222522%2F2017-06-28%2Fpost-%E3%80%90750%E3%80%91%E8%88%88%E6%A5%AD%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%9A%E6%8C%8169%E8%82%A1%E5%8F%AF%E8%AA%8D%E8%B3%BC1%E8%82%A1%E8%88%88%E6%A5%AD%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=A7hDTDjdZBMZZ4aiadAECwKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=df15367f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://vancouver.singtao.ca/1222522/2017-06-28/post-【750】興業太陽能：持69股可認購1股興業新材料/?variant=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"a345f432309aa7f93709a3380d941106cce18582","tid":302597,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T13:34:39.000Z","msg":"應去馬，定伏?"},{"pid":"dcf45a0a4d1a869d21ff6a936ffdd0d74346e701","tid":302597,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"少少錢搏創仔，可能好似漢能薄膜咁炒起?"}]}